import React,{useState,useEffect} from "react"; import classes from "./TicketProp.module.css" import {getuserbyId, getcategorybyId} from '../../../CommonApps/AllAPICalls'; import {BsFillRecordFill} from 'react-icons/bs'; const TicketProp = (props) =>{ let timeData = new Date(props.data.created_at); let timeDataStr=timeData.toString() let fulltime=timeDataStr.split(" ")[4]; let hrmin = fulltime.split(":")[0]+":"+fulltime.split(":")[1] let year = timeDataStr.split(" ")[3]; let month = timeDataStr.split(" ")[2]; let day = timeDataStr.split(" ")[1]; console.log("date: ", day); return(
    Category: {props.data.category.name}
    Priority: {props.data.priority}
    Status: { props.data.status==="open" && {props.data.status} } { props.data.status==="closed" && {props.data.status} }
    Resolution: {props.data.resolution}
    Created by : { props.data.author !==null && props.data.author.usertitle+" "+props.data.author.firstname+" "+props.data.author.lastname } { props.data.author ===null && "N/A"}
    Last updated by : Ipsita Nanda
    Visibility : All
    Created at : {props.data.created_at}
    Last updated at : June 2021
); } export default TicketProp;
